@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_LOGIN

### Profile (routes use singular "user", not "users")
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "email": "newemail@example.com"
}

### Password change step 1 — sends 6-digit OTP to email (must be logged in)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/password/request-change
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "secret12",
  "newPassword": "newsecret12"
}

### Password change step 2 — code from email
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/password/confirm-change
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "123456"
}

### Activity summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/activity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
